        "format": "",
        "indent": 0,
        "type": "heading",
        "tag": "h3",
        "version": 1
      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "On a brighter note, regulators at the FTC appear intent on cracking down on PBMs. In June, the FTC launched an investigation into the business practices of the six largest vertically integrated PBMs, to evaluate how these business arrangements impact prescription drug access and affordability.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
