          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Sen. Maria Cantwell (D-Wash.) recently introduced the Pharmacy Benefit Manager Transparency Act of 2022 alongside Sen. Chuck Grassley (R-Iowa), who had ",
