            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": " to open an investigation into PBMs. The legislation seeks to hold PBMs accountable for their deceptive practices by banning spread pricing and encouraging greater transparency. Unfortunately, the current bill ",
